00:02:11.180 --> 00:02:13.830
This prompts Christian to ask if she has an
actual question for him.

00:02:13.830 --> 00:02:17.930
Then, Ana clumsily blurts out, "Are you gay,"
making the both of them chuckle awkwardly.

00:02:17.930 --> 00:02:21.459
Ana apologizes for the question, explaining
that Kate wrote it, but Christian does reply

00:02:21.459 --> 00:02:22.860
